- Share list with other Nextcloud users
- Set a list as default in the app
	- if there's a default, the app opens to it
	- if no default, open to list of lists
	- Can easily get to list of lists from open list
- text input box on list screen
	- item name, quantity, check box
	- only item name is required
	- check box unfilled by default
	- list "remembers" previous items and suggests them
- tap on item to edit it or add a "location" or a "note"
- sweep icon to clear a list of purchased items
